
{% comment %}

    This snippet generates the structure of a comment.
    It is used to show not only recent comments, but also comments that were
    just published but not yet approved.

    More information:
     - http://docs.shopify.com/themes/liquid-variables/comment

{% endcomment %}

<div class="comment-head">  
    <span class="comment__meta-item">{{ comment.created_at | time_tag: format: 'date' }}</span>
    <span class="comment__meta-item">{{ comment.author }}</span>
</div>
<div class="comment-content">
    {{ comment.content }}
</div>